project structure 

/ansible-multi-device-config  
├── playbooks/  
│   └── deploy_configs.yml    # Your main YAML file  
├── inventory/  
│   ├── hosts.ini            # Device groups (Cisco)  
│   └── host_vars/           # Device-specific vars (optional)  
├── roles/                   # From Ansible Galaxy  
│   ├── cisco_ntp/           # Example: `ansible-galaxy install author.role`  
│   └── juniper_vlans/  
├── README.md                # Docs + usage  
└── requirements.txt         # Dependencies (ansible>=2.14)  
